Hey MogoMembers! Here are the latest updates we've made to the Mogo app:

• Rockstar contest: You could win up to $10,000 just for monitoring your credit score, so make sure you're opted into credit score updates! For full contest details, visit mogo.ca/rockstar.

• More free money: Refer a friend to Mogo and get $5 per referral. Plus, you'll both have a chance to win one of two cash prizes in the Rockstar contest!

And of course, the usual bug fixes and performance improvements.
